  <brief_title>A Study of Oral Dosing of ASP0456 in Patients With Chronic Constipation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase III Study of ASP0456 - A Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Parallel-group, Comparative Study and Open-label, Non-comparative Long-term Study in Patients With Chronic Constipation (Not Including Constipation Due to Organic Diseases) -</official_title>
