  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to verify the efficacy and investigate the safety of the study
      drug when ASP0456 is administered orally for 4 weeks and 52 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study consists of two parts. In Part I, ASP0456 or placebo will be administered orally
      in a blind manner. In Part II, the long-term safety and efficacy of ASP0456 will be evaluated
      in patients who have participated in the study and completed the Part I.
    </textblock>
